{
  "stem": "4247.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a horrible situation because we knew that there's not much we can do about it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what is-- what was happening, right, I mean, you must know the, the, the political and military constellation of the time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hitler, as we were saying earlier, was, was winning, right.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was successful, increasingly so, until the Russians stopped them in Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Paulus Army, you know, suffered a tremendous setback.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hundreds of Germans had been taken as prisoners.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We know it now, right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We sensed it then.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That-- because the, the, the official-- the official notification wasn't as clear as today.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You didn't have the CNN on the-- what's her name on the spot there and providing you with on-the-spot information.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a highly, highly artificial information, whatever the censor managed to get through.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And how it was worded, had hardly any, any connection with the actual event.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But you could read between the lines.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And you realized that they have gone through Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Indeed, they haven't even occupied Stalingrad, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We knew that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we sensed that there is going to be a, a turnaround.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the fear.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, now, by the time-- by the time we have realized-- you see, [SIGHS] human beings are always-- are always hoping, always optimistic, right.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We always have been-- and we're, we're part of that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have been always hoping that somehow it would not happen to us, right.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew what happened in Slovakia, because by that time-- I had relatives who came from Slovakia, like, like, like, like, wild animals, right, who have been dislodged from their habitat, right?",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
